.fi
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /etc/portage/package.use/
Directory where Yuno creates individual .use files for each package.
If this is a file instead of a directory, Yuno will convert it for you~
.TP
.I /etc/portage/package.use/*.use
Individual USE flag files created by Yuno. Named after the package
(e.g., openssl.use, gnupg.use).
.TP
.I /etc/portage/package.accept_keywords/
Directory where Yuno creates keyword unmask files.
.TP
.I /etc/portage/package.accept_keywords/*.accept_keywords
Individual keyword files for packages needing ~amd64 or **.
